                            |    Factory workers at a ceramic factory in #[u Neuquén], #[u Argentina] are preparing to defend their autonomous running of their #[strong workplace], as the courts start to look at #[strong appointing] an owner.  The workers have been running the factory strong since the Argentinian government #[strong meltdown] in 2001, and say they are more effective working independently.
